  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "GGP will basically build on the already developed tools like; Public Hearings, Citizen Report Card, Citizen Complaint platform, the Help-Line, Nepali bulletins, Radio Programmes and local FM radios, adapting these tools to the new priorities. The training and capacity building of youths, user groups, beneficiaries, frontline service providers, VDC and line agency officials in the use and application of these instruments for the effective service delivery and empowerment of people will be the key focus of the project"
    },
